 these matters and how they apply in the training of teaching profile that we are forming. It is concluded that with the use of technology teacher becomes familiar with it, and that your domain can cause him to take a fresh look about it, we investigate the use of technology can help in producing changes in teaching practice. Keywords: Mathematics education. Teacher training. Education and Technology. },
